name: Pad Thai
description: Pad Thai is a flavorful Thai stir-fried noodle dish made with rice noodles, tofu, shrimp or chicken, bean sprouts, peanuts, and eggs, seasoned with a blend of tamarind, fish sauce, and palm sugar.

name: Margherita Pizza
description: The Margherita pizza is a traditional Italian pizza topped with fresh, ripe tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, fresh basil leaves, and a drizzle of extra-virgin olive oil on a thin, crispy crust.

name: Chicken Tikka Masala
description: Chicken Tikka Masala is a popular Indian dish consisting of marinated and grilled chicken pieces, served in a rich, creamy, and spiced tomato sauce.

name: Caesar Salad
description: A classic Caesar Salad consists of crisp romaine lettuce, croutons, shaved parmesan cheese, and is dressed with a zesty Caesar dressing.

name: Beef Stir-Fry
description: The Beef Stir-Fry is a delectable Chinese dish featuring thinly sliced beef, stir-fried with a colorful array of fresh vegetables such as bell peppers, broccoli, and carrots.

name: Lasagna
description: A classic Italian dish, Lasagna features layers of wide pasta sheets, Bolognese sauce made with ground meat and tomatoes, creamy béchamel sauce, and a generous amount of melted cheese.

name: Shrimp Tacos
description: Shrimp Tacos are a Mexican delight consisting of succulent grilled or sautéed shrimp nestled in warm tortillas.

name: Chicken Alfredo
description: Chicken Alfredo is a sumptuous Italian dish featuring fettuccine pasta generously coated in a velvety Alfredo sauce.

name: Fish and Chips
description: Fish and Chips is a traditional British dish consisting of fresh, flaky white fish, typically cod or haddock, dipped in a light, crispy batter and deep-fried until golden.

name: Miso Soup
description: Miso Soup is a traditional Japanese soup made from dashi stock, a soybean paste called miso, tofu cubes, seaweed, and chopped green onions.

name: Tandoori Chicken
description: Tandoori Chicken is a well-known Indian dish made by marinating chicken in a blend of yogurt and aromatic spices.

name: Ramen Bowl
description: A steaming bowl of Ramen, a Japanese noodle soup, served in a flavorful broth with slices of tender pork, a soft-boiled egg, seaweed, and chopped green onions.

name: BBQ Ribs
description: BBQ Ribs are succulent, slow-cooked pork ribs coated in a smoky barbecue sauce.

name: Hawaiian Pizza
description: Hawaiian Pizza features a thin crust topped with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, ham, and chunks of pineapple.

name: Pho
description: Pho is a traditional Vietnamese noodle soup made with a flavorful broth, rice noodles, and thinly sliced beef or chicken.

name: Falafel Wrap
description: A Falafel Wrap consists of crispy chickpea falafel balls tucked into warm pita bread, along with hummus, fresh vegetables, and a drizzle of tahini sauce.

name: Steak Frites
description: Steak Frites is a classic French dish featuring a tender, grilled steak served with a generous portion of golden and crispy French fries.

name: Eggplant Parmesan
description: Eggplant Parmesan consists of sliced eggplant pieces that are breaded, fried until golden, and layered with marinara sauce and melted cheese.

name: Spaghetti Carbonara
description: A classic Italian pasta dish made with spaghetti, eggs, Pecorino Romano cheese, pancetta, and black pepper.

name: Sushi Combo
description: An assorted selection of sushi including nigiri and maki rolls.
